CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 10, 1953, pg. 21 reads: "They'll Be Living Here - These are some of the families which have purchased homes in Belmar Gardens. First occupancy is expected early next spring."
TitMainTitle: Crowd of men, children, and women, including one wearing floral shirt and striped skirt, holding shoulders of girl, standing on site of Belmar Gardens for groundbreaking, with light colored tent, American flag, and trees
